  "title": "feat: composition",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR currently adds support for Composition using a (currently not published yet) Composition API Client:\r\n- new `compositionID` optional parameter when initializing InstantSearch (this PR)\r\n- don't allow index widget when in composition mode #6459\r\n- make composition compatible with vue #6458\r\n- handle disjunctive facets #6485\r\n- add searchForFacetValues #6489\r\n- make composition work server-side + typing #6509 \r\n- tests #6510\r\n",
